      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented V&V test suite with traceability to release version; configuration management records required.",
      "rationale": "Commercial CFD solver has partial SQA documentation. Version control records exist but test suite coverage does not extend to the hemolysis sub-model. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
